<div class="cont-main">
  <h1>About Us</h1>
  <div class="cont">
    <p>
        Funfooding.com is online and mobile platform for trading home cooked food in the local community. The idea is to provide diners with unlimited varied options available in and around their vicinity. In other words, in your neck of the woods.<br />
 
        A diner can place an order a takeout for an immediate or scheduled for later with the option to pick up or get delivered.
        <br /><br />
        Want home cooked food but not in the mood to cook <br />
        Search for people in your area who is sharing their meal at that hour.
          <br /><br />
        <b>We aspire to make your fooding experience fun!</b>
        Have new ideas? @Html.ActionLink("Talk", "Contact", "Company") to us. We are all ears!
         
  </div>

</div>
